<h3 id="运行gulp项目报错task-function-must-be-specified">运行gulp项目报错：Task function must be specified</h3>

<p>原因：出现这个错误的原因是，gulp全局插件(CLI version)和项目中(Local version)的版本号不一致</p>

<pre><code class="language-git">Betters-iMac:use-gulp-build-project better$ gulp -v
[10:08:41] CLI version 3.9.1
[10:08:41] Local version 4.0.0
</code></pre>

<p>解决方案：重装gulp，统一版本号</p>

<pre><code class="language-git">npm install gulp@3.9.1 --save-dev
</code></pre>
